f'(x) = n(1+x)^{n-1}
f''(x)=n(n-1)(1+x)^{n-2}
f(x):=\sum_{i=0}^n {n\choose i}x^i = (1+x)^n.
xf'(x)=\sum_{i=0}^n {n\choose i}ix^i
x (f'(x)+xf''(x))=\sum_{i=0}^n {n\choose i}i^2x^i
